At 09:32 5/23/03 -0400, Kelly wrote:
>~Kelly, also assuming she's performing again Saturday night!

I plan to, Kelly; that talent show was a lot of fun last year. The WHOLE
thing was a lot of fun! (Well, at least for those of us who didn't slip and
fall and break our ankles and spend the whole conference in pain and
misery. I think only one of us did that and didn't have any fun. The rest
of us...)

Marji, who is really looking forward to an official count of how many
unschooling moms are named Kelly or Kelli and Robin or Robyn and Pam, and
meeting them all. (Told ya I was tired! I crack really bad jokes when I'm
tired. It's kind of like a Tourette's syndrome or something,
uncontrollable bad-joke-cracking and pun-making. Maybe I should go back to
bed!e)
